    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. i'm hearing a lot from local owners that these aren't just \"upgrades\" but basically impossible costs that are gonna force people to shut down or move out of the district. do you think the \"long term innovation\" argument is a realistic way to look at it for a business that's struggling to stay afloat right now?",
